@startuml
!include ../../_common/style.puml

title 旧 Owner 写入被 Fencing Token 拒绝

participant Client as DefaultDistributedLockClient
participant Callback
participant Guard as FencingTokenGuard
participant Repository
database DB
participant Handle as DefaultLockHandle

Client -> Callback : doWithLock(handle token=10)
Callback -> Guard : requireAccepted(handle, conditionalWrite)
Guard -> Repository : updateIfNewer(token=10)
Repository -> DB : UPDATE ... WHERE last_token < 10
DB --> Repository : affectedRows=0\n(current token=11)
Repository --> Guard : false
Guard --> Callback : throw FencingTokenRejectedException
Callback --> Client : exception
Client -> Handle : releaseWithOutcome()
Client --> Client : LockResult(FENCING_REJECTED, FENCING, acquired=true)

note right of DB
  拒绝发生在最终资源端，
  因此即使旧进程恢复也不能覆盖新结果。
end note

@enduml
